Package: rabbitvcs-dfm
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, rabbitvcs-cli, dde-file-manager
Description: RabbitVCS integration for DDE File Manager
 RabbitVCS is a graphical front-end to version control systems like SVN, Git,
 and Mercurial. This package integrates RabbitVCS into the DDE File Manager
 (dde-file-manager), providing context menu actions and emblem icons for
 version-controlled files.
